[
    {
        "source_sentence": "弊魔試目連經一名魔嬈亂經",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吳月支國居士支謙譯",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，佛遊於焚祇國妙華山恐懼聚鹿",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "苑中。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，賢者大目乾連，夜於冥中經行，由於平路經行往返。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於時，弊魔往詣佛所，自化徹景入目連腹中。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者大目乾連：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「吾腹何故而作雷鳴？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如飢人而負重擔。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾將入室正受三昧，觀察其源。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是目連即入其室三昧觀身，即時覩見弊魔作化徹景入其腹中，即謂之曰：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「弊魔！",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "且出且出！",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "莫嬈如來及其弟子，將無長夜獲苦不安墜于惡趣。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」魔心念言：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今此沙門，未會見我亦不知我，橫造妄語：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『弊魔！",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "且出且出！",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勿嬈如來及其弟子，將無長夜獲苦不安。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』正使其師大聖世尊，尚不知吾，況其弟子？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」目連報曰：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「吾復知復知卿今心所念：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『其師大聖尚不能知，況其弟子，知吾所在耶？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」魔即恐懼：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今此沙門已覺我矣！",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a19_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即化徹身出住其前。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "目連告魔：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「乃往過去久遠之世，拘樓秦佛時，我曾為魔，號曰瞋恨。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾有一姉，名曰黤黑，爾時汝為作子，以是知之，是吾姉子。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時有佛出于世間，號拘樓秦如來、至真、等正覺，有二弟子，一曰洪音，二曰知想，最尊第一仁賢難及。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何故賢者名曰洪音？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "住於梵天謦揚大聲，聞于三千大千世界。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何故賢者名知想？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若處閑居，坐於樹下、曠野山中，如其色像三昧正受。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "牧羊牧牛、擔薪負草、田居行人，見之如此，各相謂言：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867a29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『於此命過，吾等各各輦薪負草，共蛇維之。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』如其所言，即共蛇維。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知想比丘從三昧起，奮迅衣服去其埃灰，更整法服，持鉢入城國邑聚落而行分衛。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b03_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "牧牛羊者負薪草人，心懷驚愕各各相謂：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『吾在曠野閑居，見此比丘，坐於樹下而不喘息，謂之命過，共積薪草而蛇維之。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』今者知想，以是之故曰想識。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於是瞋恚魔心自念言：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『此輩沙門自謂持戒，寂然默聲思惟而行，譬如狗猫思欲捕鼠，靜然不動鼠出即搏，沙門禪思亦復如是。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如鶬鶴而欲捕魚，默靜聲潛思魚出則吞，諸沙門等亦復如是，潛思惟念專有所求。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大驢晝負重駄至夜疲極，飢渴潛思欲得食飲，諸沙門等亦復如是。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「時，魔心念：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我寧可化於此國土長者梵志，取諸持戒沙門道人，撾捶罵詈、裂衣破鉢破頭。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b15_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令起瞋恚，吾因是緣得其方便。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』尋如所念，即化國中長者梵志，取諸沙門持戒奉法，撾捶罵詈、壞鉢破頭、裂其被服。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸沙門，如猫捕鼠如鶴吞魚，譬如鵄梟於樹間捕鼠，諸沙門坐禪亦復如是，如驢飢疲。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時諸比丘，皆被毀辱低頭直行，至拘樓秦佛所。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛為四輩天龍鬼神廣說經道，見諸比丘被毀辱來，告諸比丘：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『比丘！",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今瞋恨魔化諸國中長者梵志，取諸持戒奉法沙門，撾捶罵詈、破頭壞鉢、裂其衣服，令心變恨起瞋恚意，吾以是緣得其方便使道不成。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾等於此，當行四等：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慈、悲、喜、護，不懷怨結，無瞋恨心，廣大難限普安無邊等于十方，雖求汝便終不能得。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』比丘受教，所在閑居曠野一心禪思，行四等心意無增減。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867b29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時瞋恚魔，雖求持戒奉法沙門之便，永不能得。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時長者梵志從受魔教，毀辱持戒奉法沙門，壽終之後皆歸惡趣，勤苦瘦惱考掠之處。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "在地獄中受其化身，譬如大樹，其廣大如大曠野，在燒鐵地裸形自投，各自謂言：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『吾等薄祐殃暴弊惡，乃取持戒奉法沙門毀辱罵詈，吾等於此歸命呼嗟，不能得見持戒奉法沙門，欲求其便因緣相見，已自造此自獲其殃，坐隨魔教不能護身。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「爾時，瞋恚魔心自念言：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『因是方便，求諸沙門持戒人便，永不能得；",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "必當變行，化諸長者梵志，供養奉侍持戒沙門，衣被飯食床臥醫藥，使貪供養，因是之緣吾得其便。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』尋如其計，即化國中長者梵志，所在行路四徼道中，若在街曲，見諸持戒沙門道人，布髮著地令行其上，皆口稱曰：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『持戒沙門，修身勤行，難值難遇，唯蹈吾髮，使我長夜得福無量。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』持擎衣服，往造其所，稽首長跪：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願見愍傷，受此衣服。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c18_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』笥籢盛食，詣就精舍，若街巷里頭供奉上供養：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c19_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『持戒沙門難值難遇，願受此供，使我長夜得福無量。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』抱之擎之，若負擔之輿之，歸於其舍，坐著好床，出諸飯食衣服袈裟金銀七寶，而著其前，長跪白曰：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『持戒沙門難值難見，願受此供，唯見愍傷，恣意所欲，使我長夜得福無量。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「時拘樓秦佛為諸四輩諸天龍神，見諸持戒沙門道士，為諸長者梵志所見供養敬事無量。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "告諸比丘：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『今瞋恚魔！",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0867c27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "化諸長者梵志，使供養持戒沙門道士，衣被飯食床臥醫藥，恣意所欲使著供養，吾因是緣得其方便，壞其善心使道不成。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝等所由閑居巖處曠野，念諸萬物所在無常，雖著衣食莫以貪樂，苦空非身，魔雖求便終不能得。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』諸比丘即受拘樓秦如來、至真、等正覺教，行之如法，魔雖求便永不能得。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「魔所教化長者梵志，使令供養持戒沙門，由此之德皆生天上。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生天上已，各心念言：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『吾等供養奉法沙門持戒清淨，自獲是福，不由他人，非天所與。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「爾時，拘樓秦佛如來、至真、等正覺，飯食之後以日昳時，與大弟子洪音俱行遊於郡縣。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於時，弊魔化作大人為勇猛士，手執大棒住于道側，竊舉大棒擊洪音頭，破頭灑血其血流離，爾時辟䨴在世尊後，如影隨形默聲無言。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a13_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時拘樓秦如來無極大聖，還顧歎息，口演此言：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『今瞋恚魔！",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知節限所造大過。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』時瞋恚魔，即以此身墮沒地獄，宛轉地獄，如魚蝌蚪出水在於陸地，譬如生剝牛皮，宛轉在地痛不可言。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時魔波旬，在於地獄宛轉毒痛，又過於此億千萬倍，譬若如人，身得狂病走不安處。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a19_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「時魔波旬，墮大地獄苦痛無量，時泥梨傍往語之言：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『子欲知之，若有一籌，一鳥飛現，知過十千萬歲，如是之比亦復難限。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "弊魔！",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾在地獄壽數如是，然後乃從大地獄出，更復遭厄二萬餘歲。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』爾時，弊魔甚大愁毒。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a24_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛為目連說此偈言：",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「瞋魔所受罪，　　其地獄何類？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘樓秦佛時，　　化眾及弟子。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所可受患惱，　　一切見考治。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "火然自燒身，　　其㷿面繞形，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其地獄如斯，　　瞋恚魔所在。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘樓秦佛時，　　洪音大弟子，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使在佛前，　　及觀比丘眾，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "因由緣受罪，　　斯須得動擾。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設有喜評相，　　比丘佛弟子，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "必當獲此殃，　　趣於極苦患。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如人投深淵，　　捨於天宮殿，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不在玉女間，　　棄於天上樂。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其有曉了此，　　比丘佛弟子，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自興從已出，　　危害墮苦患。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "魔當知吾身，　　倚於解脫門，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不天處天人，　　忉利名聞天。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使分別此，　　比丘佛弟子，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自身犯非法，　　因此歸惡趣。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其以一足指，　　動搖最勝宮，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所處神足力，　　目連大感應。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其有曉了此，　　比丘佛弟子，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身自為興立，　　安能墮惡趣。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設端正有百，　　微妙好玉女，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見比丘禪思，　　彼不住園觀。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使分別此，　　比丘佛弟子，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘自造行，　　或能歸惡趣。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使等和同，　　詣帝釋問事，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "天帝為解不？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b24_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　何因獲解脫？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "釋應時發遣，　　隨其所問答，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若自無所著，　　然後得解脫。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使曉了此，　　比丘佛弟子，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨己所作行，　　自到歸惡趣。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有至梵天，　　難問梵天王，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何因致是處，　　得立于梵天？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "梵天即答曰，　　隨問而發遣，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今吾所立處，　　未曾懷邪見。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從梵天普見，　　光明有退轉，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾今當何說，　　我身長存乎？",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使曉了此，　　比丘佛弟子，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身自犯非法，　　自然歸勤苦。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其火無想念，　　我當燒愚癡，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚騃自興火，　　還自危燒身。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "波旬當解此，　　用意向如來，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "還自危其身，　　如火燒癡人。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人憙為眾惡，　　長夜為己身，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "命來不自覺，　　無得嬈比丘。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "魔慎莫試佛，　　無嬈諸弟子，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長夜不安隱，　　必當歸惡趣。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於時魔降伏，　　坐恐比丘故，",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼聞此憂愁，　　應時忽不現。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說如是，諸天龍神莫不歡喜。",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "弊魔試目連經",
        "from": "T01n0067_001:0868c19_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]